---
title: Carb Smart Bison and Zucchini Skillet with Spinach and Mozzarella
description: This bison and zucchini skillet is a fresh take on a classic lasagne! Tonight, vegetables are replacing noodles. You'll layer up zucchini with saucy bison ragu and melty cheese for a light weeknight meal.

